{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":9,"day":22}],"page_start":5,"page_end":5,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"大海航行靠舵手〔朗诵诗〕","authors":["邓花绪"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日出东方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光芒照四海——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的祖国顶天立地站起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨人的双手，英雄的气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"概，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把万里江山重新安排。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，伟大的领袖毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们对您无限忠诚、无限"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热爱、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无限信仰、无限崇拜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海航行靠舵手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命航道巨人开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回忆那艰苦的岁月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心潮滚滚，汹涌澎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湃——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从秋收起义军号响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到天安门上红旗摆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的领袖付出了多少心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来把今天的幸福红花灌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昆仑高上天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大江入东海。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用毛泽东思想武装的中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉碎时代的逆流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踢开脚下的障碍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把革命推向前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让胜利传遍全世界。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，大寨的红花开遍全"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大庆的革命精神传开来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原子弹、氢弹震天响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞溅的钢花开不败，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万个雷锋又站起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一代新人接班来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，伟大的统帅毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带领我们走向光辉灿烂的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级专政要巩固，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的江山不能变色！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的领袖毛主席挥巨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命的烈火燃起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想伟大红旗高高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个祖国焕发出更灿烂的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百万革命小将冲锋陷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彻底清除污泥浊水的旧世"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"界。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"资本主义复辟的一枕黄粱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被粉碎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揪出了党内最大的一小撮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走资本主义道路的当权"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国赫鲁晓夫变成了“落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水狗”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"资产阶级司令部彻底垮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但冻僵的毒蛇还在准备咬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那装死的老虎还要伺机反"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扑过来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要拿起笔作刀枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从政治上、思想上、理论"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彻底批倒、批臭党内最大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的一小撮走资本主义道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路的当权派。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们紧跟伟大统帅毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的战略部署，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在革命大批判中促进革命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大联合，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实现革命的“三结合”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进行斗批改。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们高举“拥军爱民”的大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为革命立新功！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将无产阶级文化大革命进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行到底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做彻底的无产阶级革命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"派！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地起风雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里云雾开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的祖国把反帝、反修"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大旗举起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们手挽五洲，心连四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界的朋友四方来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听，非洲的战鼓咚咚响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南越的丛林里战歌多豪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五大洲人民齐声欢呼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界进入毛泽东思想的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大新时代！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是毛主席的战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是红色的新一代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辈子学习毛主席著作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命斗志永远不衰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辈子紧紧跟着毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风里不动摇，浪里不摇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定让毛泽东思想的伟大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在全世界高高飘扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让革命的火炬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传到万代千秋，千秋万"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"name":"革命三结合","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}